{"id": 239756398, "title": "Laguna Beach Car Shop Owner Accused of Stealing Cars of His Clients", "text": "SANTA ANA, Calif.\u2014The owner of an auto repair shop in Laguna Beach was behind bars Friday on charges of stealing the cars of his clients. James Michael Ross, 59, who owns Laguna Beach Collision Center, was booked into the Orange County Jail Friday and set to appear in court Monday. Mr. Ross was charged in March with defrauding another and grand theft, both felonies. He was accused of stealing a 2024 Jeep Wrangler, according to the criminal complaint. Mr. Ross pleaded guilty June 23 of last year to drunken driving. Police reported Mr. Ross was arrested in April related to six cases. Investigators allege he had stolen multiple vehicles brought in for repairs. When the car owners could not get their cars back, they called police. Police said another customer reported on Wednesday that Mr. Ross stole the person\u2019s vehicle. Anyone who believes they are a victim was asked to call investigators at 949-715-0984. Orange County Crime Stoppers will accept anonymous tips at 855-TIP-OCCS.", "summary": "SANTA ANA, Calif.\u2014The owner of an auto repair shop in Laguna Beach was behind bars Friday on charges of stealing the cars of his clients. James Michael Ross, 59, who owns Laguna Beach Collision Center, was booked into the Orange County Jail Friday and set to appear in court Monday. Mr. Ross was charged in [&#8230;]", "url": "https://www.theepochtimes.com/us/laguna-beach-car-shop-owner-accused-of-stealing-cars-of-his-clients-5673772", "image": "https://img.theepochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2021/08/01/Police-Siren_JF_04012021-2-300x180.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-23 01:10:28", "author": "City News Service", "authors": ["City News Service"], "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "us", "sentiment": -0.718}